column16: Matt Adams singles on a line drive to right fielder Jay Bruce.   Yadier Molina to 3rd.
Yadier Molina grounds into a force out, shortstop Zack Cozart to second baseman Brandon Phillips.   Allen Craig out at 2nd.    Yadier Molina to 1st.
Allen Craig singles on a line drive to center fielder Billy Hamilton.   Matt Holliday scores.
Matt Holliday doubles (2) on a line drive to right fielder Jay Bruce.   Peter Bourjos scores.
Peter Bourjos doubles (1) on a ground ball to left fielder Ryan Ludwick.
Matt Carpenter grounds out, second baseman Brandon Phillips to first baseman Joey Votto.
Umpire reviewed (home run), call on the field was upheld: Matt Holliday singles on a line drive to right fielder Jay Bruce.   Matt Carpenter to 3rd.    Kolten Wong to 2nd.
Kolten Wong walks.   Matt Carpenter to 2nd.
